3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper deals with improving the performance of machine learning models.
4. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is possible as the paper mentions using the approach for sampled-based training, which could be relevant for computer vision tasks.
5. cs.NEURAL (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is possible as the paper deals with neural network models and their training.
